	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Debuff</strong></p><ul><li><p>If the target has 150 hit points or fewer, it is &amp;reference[Stunned]. At the end of each of its turns, the stunned creature makes a constitution save.</p></li></ul><p><strong>[[/save CON]]{Constitution Save}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure: </strong>Target remains stunned.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> The effect ends.</p></li></ul>",
